      "widgets_values": [
        "ℹ️ Edge-Aware Skin Smoother (N-03)\n- Invariant: `strength=0` → identity (pixel-exact). `mask=0` region → unchanged.\n- `sigma_color` scale is [0, 1] — NOT OpenCV 8-bit 10–50. Typical 0.05–0.3.\n- Default `strength=0.4` is a pro dose (30–50%). Never run at 1.0 on skin.\n- Mask pin is optional — connect the N-02 refined_mask upstream to gate\n  smoothing to the skin region (SAM/rembg → N-02 → N-03.mask).\n- CPU is very slow at 2K (see T-07 bench). GPU strongly recommended.\n- For the full invariant and edge cases, see test_smoother.py."
